  "text": "To evaluate the performance of the proposed method in terms of speed and accuracy, the approximated method (AM) which is based on heuristic search was used to find the suitable location and size of DG. Heuristic search is a general method of problem solving, fixing things, or for obtaining knowledge. Learning doesn't happen from failure itself but rather from analyzing the failure, making a change, and then trying again. This method has been implemented based on the principle of power flow [CITATION_1] .",
